The property is situated in Barcoo Street, Chatswood/Roseville, accessed off a major arterial road - Penshurst Street, just a few minutes from the Pacific Highway and Chatswood CBD.

The premises is ideal for small businesses, importers, trades, light manufacturers and service industries.

The estate comprises of a modern fifty-unit office/warehouse complex, featuring an on-site café and childcare centre.

The available unit is north-east facing, with a popular split of office and warehouse accommodation.

The ground floor under croft area is glazed and could be used for pick/pack or converted to a showroom. At the rear, the amenities are located including M/F bathroom and kitchenette

Features: 

- Clear span warehouse with 7m* clearance throughout
